name: d3fine
description: D3fine is a React based app that allows users to create customized personality assessments that can be shared to other users. Full CRUD technology with Firebase authentication embedded.

name: Stop Jockin
description: Stop Jockin is a platform for New Orleans local business owner , 'Joc' , used to display many of his business ventures! This app utilizes a React front-end framework, connected to a backend API that allows admin users to manage rendered data.

name: SVGeezy
description: Svgeezy is a Scalable Vector Graphic (SVG) gallery created through an Angular Framework. The goal for this app is to amass a collection of SVG images with direct svg pathing for devs to use for their projects.

name: ShipvsShip
description: Topdown player vs player space shooter made with GML. Controls: Player1- WSAD for movement, R for primary fire and space for secondary. Player2- Directional Keys for movement, primary fire with M.

name: Lightlite
description: Mock (but currently live and functional) retail store showcasing products. Includes chat support functionality, payment processing, and email subscription options.

name: gameQ
description: gameQ is an app designed for twitch streamers to be able to choose games from a large third party api, and be able to present their favorites to their followers!.
